            , spinster, was indicted for <rs id="t17721209-9-off45" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17721209-9-off45" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17721209-9-off45" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a silver tea spoon, value 2 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17721209-9-victim126" type="victimName">
                     William
                      Mackintosh
                  <interp inst="t17721209-9-victim126" type="surname" value="Mackintosh"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17721209-9-victim126" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17721209-9-victim126" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17721209-9-off45 t17721209-9-victim126"></join>
